                           @{b}@{u} Instructions @{ub}@{uu}

     Hmm... I don't think you will need any instructions, but here are
     some tips:
          
   1. The object of the game is: In one player mode to collect points.
                                 In two player mode to kill your opponent.

   2. You will crash and die if you run into walls or yourself
      our you opponent. Although...

   3. ...it is possible to run over yourself without dying if you go
      diagonaly in a cross (like an " X ") Your odds are 50%   ;-)
            
   4. Not all the items are good items! Read @{" Action items " Link "The items"}

   5. If The game is too hard, try playing with "PC SPEED" (slower :)
    
@EndNode
