                           @{b}@{u} How to install @{ub}@{uu}

     Just unpack or copy the game where you want it to be.

     You have to copy the fonts to the fonts drawer!
     
     To install new levels just copy the files to the X_Levels drawer.
     For a new level to work you need atleast three files:
     
     Level.B  Level.M  and  Level.tune
     
     You can also have a highscore file (should be in hiscore drawer.)
     and an image file: Level.IM (in X_Levels drawer).
     
     
