                           @{b}@{u} Hotkeys @{ub}@{uu}


     F1  - Starts the current level in 1ply mode.
     
     F2  - Starts 2ply "normal" mode.
     
     F3  - Starts 2ply "snake" mode.
     
     F9  - Shows the current 2ply match standings.
     
     F10 - Resets current 2ply standings: 0 - 0
     
     Esc - Takes you back to "Main menu".
     
